[normal]is
[normal] oil and gas or construction. It just seems to be an industry set up for conflict
[normal],
[normal] and that is what has happened.
[normal]              
[normal]The Rail Delivery Group is a first step in saying to an organisation that we are still bound by contract. None of that has changed. There is Schedule 4, Schedule 8, performance me
[normal]asures, the regulator and the DF
[normal]T. We still have an enormous amount of scrutiny driving performance
[normal],
